2) No DB records found for following query: 
/* My TO-DO List assignment data AD DB*/
WITH
      nextVideoLessons AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT appld.ap_grade, appld.ap_end_dt, assign.apref, assign.subject, 
               min(assign.lesson_number - CASE
                                            WHEN applc.ap_sem = 2
                                             AND tenop.eno_sem > 0
                                             AND appld.ap_1sem != 'Y' THEN 170 - subj.duration
                                            ELSE 0
                                          END) OVER (PARTITION BY assign.subject, assign.apref) AS nextVideoLesson
            FROM homeschoolhouse.student_assignments assign 
            JOIN homeschoolhouse.student_assignments_types types 
              ON assign.assignment_type_fk = types.assignment_type_pk 
            JOIN linc.abadb_appld appld 
              ON assign.apref = appld.ap_apref 
            JOIN enrollment.media_format_types mft
              ON appld.media_format_type_id = mft.media_format_type_id
            JOIN linc.abadb_applc applc
              ON appld.ap_apref = applc.apc_apref
             AND assign.subject = applc.ap_item
            JOIN linc.abadb_tenop tenop
              ON tenop.eno_subj = applc.ap_item
            JOIN homeschoolhouse.vsubjects subj
              ON subj.seriesno = tenop.eno_series
             AND subj.seriesversion = tenop.eno_ver
            LEFT JOIN linc.abadb_rchdr rchdr 
              ON appld.ap_apref = rchdr.rch_apref
           WHERE assign.student_id = '430353'
             AND appld.ap_status = 8
             AND mft.name = 'STREAMING'
             AND trunc(appld.ap_end_dt) >= trunc(sysdate) 
             AND assign.completion_date IS NULL 
             AND types.name = 'VIDEO' 
             AND (rchdr.rch_status IN ('A', 'I') OR appld.ap_credt != 'Y') 
           GROUP BY appld.ap_grade, appld.ap_end_dt, assign.apref, assign.subject, assign.lesson_number, applc.ap_sem, tenop.eno_sem, appld.ap_1sem, subj.duration
      ),
      studentAssignments AS (
        SELECT appld.ap_grade, appld.ap_end_dt, assign.apref, assign.student_assignments_id AS eventID, assign.start_date, assign.end_date, tenop.eno_desc, tboxd.txd_desc, tboxm.txm_desc, types.description, assign.completion_date, assign.lock_assignment,
               assign.da_enddate,tboxh.txh_type, assign.segment_id_fk, coalesce(to_number(assign.da_testid), tboxd.txd_da_testid, tboxm.txm_da_testid, 0) AS linkitTestID, assign.da_testassignmentid, types.name, tenop.eno_ver, tenop.eno_series,
               tboxh.txh_subj, assign.subject, assign.pr_form, assign.pr_version, assign.pr_school, assign.pr_boxletter, assign.pr_itemnumber, COALESCE(assign.pr_subitemnumber, 0) AS pr_subitemnumber, coalesce(to_number(tboxm.txm_lesson), to_number(tboxd.txd_lesson)) as lesson_number, appld.ap_ograde
          FROM homeschoolhouse.student_assignments assign
          JOIN homeschoolhouse.student_assignments_types types
            ON assign.assignment_type_fk = types.assignment_type_pk
          JOIN linc.abadb_appld appld
            ON assign.apref = appld.ap_apref
           AND appld.fd_id = '430353'
          LEFT JOIN linc.abadb_digital_assessments digAsmts
            ON assign.apref = digAsmts.application_number
           AND assign.subject = digAsmts.eno_subj
          JOIN linc.abadb_tenop tenop
            ON assign.subject = tenop.eno_subj
          LEFT JOIN linc.abadb_tboxh tboxh
            ON assign.pr_form = tboxh.txh_form
           AND assign.pr_version = tboxh.txh_ver
           AND assign.pr_school = tboxh.txh_school
           AND assign.pr_boxletter = tboxh.txh_boxltr
          LEFT JOIN linc.abadb_tboxd tboxd
            ON tboxh.txh_form = tboxd.form_number
           AND tboxh.txh_school = tboxd.school
           AND tboxh.txh_boxltr = tboxd.box_letter
           AND tboxh.txh_ver = tboxd.version
           AND assign.pr_itemnumber = tboxd.txd_itmnbr
           AND coalesce(assign.pr_subitemnumber, 0) = 0
          LEFT JOIN linc.abadb_tboxm tboxm
            ON tboxh.txh_form = tboxm.form_number
           AND tboxh.txh_school = tboxm.school
           AND tboxh.txh_boxltr = tboxm.box_letter
           AND tboxh.txh_ver = tboxm.version
           AND assign.pr_itemnumber = tboxm.txm_itmnbr
           AND assign.pr_subitemnumber = tboxm.txm_sub_itmnbr
          LEFT JOIN linc.abadb_rchdr rchdr
            ON appld.ap_apref = rchdr.rch_apref
           AND rchdr.rch_id = '430353'
         WHERE assign.student_id = '430353'
           AND types.name IN('DIGITAL-ASSESSMENT', 'PE ACTIVITY', 'PE SKILLS TEST')
           AND coalesce(assign.grade_percentage, 0) != 333.3
           AND trunc(sysdate) BETWEEN coalesce(to_date(appld.ap_beg_dt,'yyyymmdd') - 14, digAsmts.start_date) AND coalesce(appld.ap_end_dt, digAsmts.end_date)
           AND coalesce(to_number(tboxm.txm_lesson), to_number(tboxd.txd_lesson)) BETWEEN coalesce(digAsmts.start_lesson, 1) AND coalesce(digAsmts.end_lesson, 180)
           AND appld.ap_status = 8
           AND (rchdr.rch_status IN ('A', 'I')
            OR  appld.ap_credt != 'Y')
           AND ('N' != 'Y' OR (coalesce(tboxd.txd_da_testid, tboxm.txm_da_testid, 0) > 0 AND ap_ograde = 'Y'))
      ),
      nextLessons AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT assign.ap_grade, assign.ap_end_dt, assign.txh_subj, MIN(to_number(assign.lesson_number)) OVER (PARTITION BY assign.txh_subj) AS nextLesson
          FROM studentAssignments assign
         WHERE assign.completion_date IS NULL
         GROUP BY assign.ap_grade, assign.ap_end_dt, assign.txh_subj, assign.lesson_number
      ),
      currentPELesson AS (
        SELECT assign.ap_grade, assign.ap_end_dt, coalesce(assign.txh_subj, assign.subject) AS subject, assign.lesson_number AS currentLesson
          FROM studentAssignments assign
         WHERE trunc(assign.start_date) = trunc(sysdate)
           AND assign.name IN ('PE ACTIVITY', 'PE SKILLS TEST')
      ),
      streamSubjects AS (
        SELECT subj.subjectid, subj.subjectname, subj.book_item_number, subj.image_url, subj.duration,
               subj.seriesno, subj.seriesversion, subj.rcg_subj,
               sTypes.supergroup, sTypes.sessionname, sTypes.sortorder
          FROM homeschoolhouse.vsubjects subj
          LEFT JOIN homeschoolhouse.vsessiontypes sTypes
            ON subj.subjectid = sTypes.subjectid
         WHERE (sTypes.sessiontypeid = (SELECT max(sessiontypeid)
                                          FROM homeschoolhouse.vsessiontypes sTypes2
                                         WHERE sTypes2.subjectid = subj.subjectid
                                           AND coalesce(sTypes2.bonus_content, 'N') != 'Y')
            OR sTypes.sessiontypeid is null)
      )

      SELECT assign.ap_grade, assign.ap_end_dt, assign.apref, assign.eventID, assign.start_date, assign.end_date, coalesce(CASE WHEN subj.supergroup IS NOT NULL then subj.subjectname ELSE coalesce(subj.sessionname, subj.subjectname) END, assign.eno_desc) AS short_description, coalesce(assign.txd_desc, assign.txm_desc, assign.description) AS long_description, assign.completion_date, assign.lock_assignment,
             box.description AS assignType, assign.segment_id_fk, linkitTestID, assign.da_testassignmentid, to_number(subj.book_item_number) AS book_item_number, subj.image_url,
             assign.subject, assign.pr_form, assign.pr_version, assign.pr_school, assign.pr_boxletter, assign.pr_itemnumber, coalesce(assign.pr_subitemnumber, 0) AS pr_subitemnumber,
             cast(coalesce(subj.sortorder, 99) AS NUMBER(3)) AS sortorder, assign.lesson_number, cast(coalesce(subj.subjectid, -1) AS NUMBER(10)) AS subject_id_fk,
             CASE
               WHEN nVL.nextVideoLesson > subj.duration THEN nVL.nextVideoLesson - subj.duration
               ELSE COALESCE(nVL.nextVideoLesson, 170)
             END AS nextVideoLesson, assign.ap_ograde
        FROM studentAssignments assign
        LEFT JOIN progress_report.pr_box_types box
          ON assign.txh_type = box.box_type
        LEFT JOIN streamSubjects subj
          ON assign.eno_series = subj.seriesno
         AND assign.eno_ver = subj.seriesversion
         AND assign.txh_subj = subj.rcg_subj
        LEFT JOIN nextLessons nLmL
          ON assign.txh_subj = nLmL.txh_subj
        LEFT JOIN nextVideoLessons nVL
          ON assign.subject = nVL.subject
        LEFT JOIN currentPELesson cPEL
          ON coalesce(assign.txh_subj, assign.subject) = cPEL.subject
       WHERE (assign.lesson_number = CASE
                                       WHEN coalesce(trim(assign.txh_type), 'PE') = 'PE' THEN cPEL.currentLesson
                                       ELSE nLmL.nextLesson
                                     END
          OR (trunc(coalesce(assign.completion_date, assign.da_enddate)) = trunc(sysdate)
         AND 'N' != 'Y'))
         AND assign.completion_date IS NULL
 DBAD
